WEBVTT

00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:20.940
=About Love=

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.940
=Episode 19=

00:01:24.280 --> 00:01:25.120
Mingming.

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:26.840
Mingming.

00:01:28.840 --> 00:01:29.680
Where are you going?

00:01:30.760 --> 00:01:31.600
Me?

00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:33.240
Home.

00:01:33.790 --> 00:01:34.630
Where else would I go?

00:01:35.710 --> 00:01:36.550
Let's go.

00:01:49.040 --> 00:01:50.590
This will pass.

00:01:51.590 --> 00:01:52.590
I'm here with you.

00:02:11.240 --> 00:02:12.190
Sen, listen to me.

00:02:12.360 --> 00:02:13.240
It's not what you think.

00:02:13.240 --> 00:02:14.240
Those photos, I…

00:02:14.800 --> 00:02:16.360
I didn't know he was married.

00:02:16.360 --> 00:02:17.430
And I didn't… I…

00:02:17.430 --> 00:02:18.470
I'm not a home-wrecker.

00:02:18.470 --> 00:02:19.560
- I know.
- I didn't know how those photos

00:02:19.560 --> 00:02:20.470
- turned out like that.
- I know, Mingming.

00:02:20.470 --> 00:02:21.630
I know, I know.

00:02:21.630 --> 00:02:23.400
- I really...
- Mingming, this isn't your fault.

00:02:24.800 --> 00:02:25.840
Are you out of your mind?

00:02:25.840 --> 00:02:26.690
What?

00:02:26.700 --> 00:02:27.870
Feeling bad for your true love?

00:02:28.190 --> 00:02:29.470
Are you happy now?

00:02:30.030 --> 00:02:31.280
Do you know this could ruin her?

00:02:31.430 --> 00:02:32.710
Do you even know you ruined me,

00:02:33.280 --> 00:02:34.240
and our family?

00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:38.190
Delete it.

00:02:39.470 --> 00:02:40.750
It's blowing up online.

00:02:41.750 --> 00:02:42.590
Why should I?

00:02:43.260 --> 00:02:44.100
(Incorrect password. Please try again.)

00:02:47.700 --> 00:02:48.700
(Incorrect password. Please try again.)

00:02:50.360 --> 00:02:51.240
What's the password?

00:02:52.310 --> 00:02:53.310
What's the password?

00:02:57.150 --> 00:02:58.030
Don't push me.

00:02:58.310 --> 00:02:59.150
Delete it!

00:02:59.280 --> 00:03:00.470
You pushed me first.

00:03:07.190 --> 00:03:08.400
You're insane!

00:03:13.630 --> 00:03:14.470
It's my fault.

00:03:15.360 --> 00:03:16.200
It's all my fault.

00:03:20.150 --> 00:03:21.310
Sorry for what I did to you.

00:03:21.750 --> 00:03:22.960
Please leave me alone.

00:03:26.120 --> 00:03:26.960
Mingming.

00:03:27.470 --> 00:03:28.400
Go away.

00:03:31.400 --> 00:03:32.910
- Mingming.
- I said go away!

00:03:33.560 --> 00:03:35.470
I'm cheap. I'm stupid.

00:03:35.990 --> 00:03:36.840
Who would ever

00:03:36.840 --> 00:03:38.240
want to be with someone like me?

00:03:39.280 --> 00:03:40.710
We're done, Sen.

00:03:41.800 --> 00:03:43.240
I don't care!

00:03:43.870 --> 00:03:44.710
Trust me.

00:03:45.150 --> 00:03:46.430
This will blow over soon.

00:03:46.590 --> 00:03:47.520
People will forget.

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:49.240
Look at everyone out there.

00:03:49.840 --> 00:03:51.030
Do they know who we are?

00:03:51.030 --> 00:03:53.080
You don't care now, but what about later?

00:03:53.310 --> 00:03:54.360
For the rest of your life,

00:03:54.360 --> 00:03:55.960
people will judge you.

00:03:55.960 --> 00:03:57.030
They'll laugh at you.

00:03:57.030 --> 00:03:58.870
Let them judge! Let them laugh!

00:03:58.870 --> 00:04:00.280
You'll end up hating me!

00:04:00.280 --> 00:04:02.400
I won't hate you. I won't!

00:04:02.400 --> 00:04:04.310
You will, and then you'll...

00:04:04.710 --> 00:04:05.840
You'll leave me.

00:04:06.590 --> 00:04:07.430
Sen,

00:04:07.710 --> 00:04:09.080
pull yourself together.

00:04:09.590 --> 00:04:11.430
- Mingming, I'll never hate you.
- Go away.

00:04:12.910 --> 00:04:14.680
- I've waited seven years for you.
- Let me go.

00:04:14.680 --> 00:04:16.270
We've been through so much to be together.

00:04:16.680 --> 00:04:17.600
No matter what happens,

00:04:17.600 --> 00:04:18.680
I'm not leaving you.

00:04:18.680 --> 00:04:20.000
I'll stay by your side.

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:22.160
I'll always be here to protect you.

00:04:22.160 --> 00:04:23.750
Don't leave me.

00:04:24.040 --> 00:04:25.270
You can't leave.

00:04:39.390 --> 00:04:40.230
Sen.

00:04:40.680 --> 00:04:41.520
Sen.

00:04:43.390 --> 00:04:44.920
I'm scared.

00:04:45.270 --> 00:04:46.720
I'm really scared.

00:04:47.510 --> 00:04:48.630
Don't be.

00:04:49.000 --> 00:04:49.840
Don't be scared.

00:04:52.630 --> 00:04:54.630
I'm not going anywhere.

00:05:19.360 --> 00:05:20.200
Yingtao,

00:05:20.340 --> 00:05:21.190
you…

00:05:21.190 --> 00:05:22.430
Oh, you have company.

00:05:23.430 --> 00:05:24.800
No wonder you didn't text me back.

00:05:27.800 --> 00:05:28.640
So?

00:05:29.270 --> 00:05:30.390
Who's she?

00:05:35.360 --> 00:05:36.430
I'm his ex-girlfriend.

00:05:40.120 --> 00:05:41.870
Guess I don't need to introduce myself.

00:05:42.240 --> 00:05:43.270
We go way back with him.

00:05:47.830 --> 00:05:49.630
She came to pick up the stuff she left behind.

00:05:51.600 --> 00:05:53.070
I've gotta go. Bye.

00:05:58.680 --> 00:06:00.390
I told her last time to take everything.

00:06:00.950 --> 00:06:02.630
But she insisted she left something.

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:06.750
I didn't tell you this

00:06:06.750 --> 00:06:08.870
because I don't want to upset you.

00:06:08.870 --> 00:06:09.710
Break up with me.

00:06:10.800 --> 00:06:11.750
I don't agree.

00:06:12.710 --> 00:06:13.570
You must get it wrong.

00:06:13.570 --> 00:06:14.480
I can explain.

00:06:17.070 --> 00:06:17.910
Check my phone.

00:06:18.430 --> 00:06:19.480
Look at all the chats.

00:06:19.480 --> 00:06:20.600
There's nothing between us.

00:06:20.600 --> 00:06:21.440
Zeyan,

00:06:22.750 --> 00:06:24.000
breaking up isn't a divorce.

00:06:24.750 --> 00:06:25.800
We don't need a reason.

00:06:56.190 --> 00:06:57.560
Surprise!

00:06:58.360 --> 00:06:59.480
Nice job, Luanluan.

00:06:59.480 --> 00:07:00.320
You nailed it!

00:07:01.240 --> 00:07:02.390
Why the long face again?

00:07:02.870 --> 00:07:04.070
I watched the whole play.

00:07:04.070 --> 00:07:04.910
Didn't leave halfway.

00:07:07.020 --> 00:07:07.860
(I'm here. See you soon.)

00:07:08.070 --> 00:07:09.070
That guy again?

00:07:09.920 --> 00:07:11.010
I've told you many times.

00:07:11.010 --> 00:07:12.620
What has he ever done for you?

00:07:12.920 --> 00:07:14.870
Look at Mr. Zhang's son.

00:07:14.880 --> 00:07:16.160
He sends you flowers every show.

00:07:16.430 --> 00:07:17.430
Roses!

00:07:17.830 --> 00:07:19.040
You know what that means?

00:07:19.430 --> 00:07:20.270
Just put it there.

00:07:28.200 --> 00:07:29.870
I'd blame Luanluan for this.

00:07:30.160 --> 00:07:31.440
She didn't tell you she gave me

00:07:31.440 --> 00:07:32.340
a ticket too?

00:07:32.360 --> 00:07:34.130
Luanluan loves stirring the pot.

00:07:34.270 --> 00:07:35.900
She cleared out three people in one play.

00:07:36.040 --> 00:07:37.880
Short on numbers for dinner. I'm starving.

00:07:37.890 --> 00:07:38.750
Though I'm late,

00:07:38.750 --> 00:07:40.430
the ending was actually nice.

00:07:40.430 --> 00:07:41.270
The beginning wasn't.

00:07:41.290 --> 00:07:42.800
Luanluan was in no position to judge.

00:07:42.800 --> 00:07:44.750
Cornered and defenseless, she passed the buck.

00:07:44.750 --> 00:07:45.590
She went too far.

00:07:45.720 --> 00:07:46.560
Way too far...

00:07:52.430 --> 00:07:54.390
I don't believe my boyfriend would betray me.

00:07:54.390 --> 00:07:56.000
I've got to have you. I've got to!

00:07:57.870 --> 00:07:59.040
You didn't expect this?

00:07:59.390 --> 00:08:00.360
Miss Diona?

00:08:01.360 --> 00:08:02.270
I didn't expect

00:08:02.750 --> 00:08:03.800
to run into you here.

00:08:06.160 --> 00:08:07.000
You know them?

00:08:07.360 --> 00:08:08.510
You've got the wrong person.

00:08:10.630 --> 00:08:11.920
The name might be fake.

00:08:12.160 --> 00:08:13.430
How could we possibly know

00:08:13.430 --> 00:08:14.430
your real name?

00:08:15.830 --> 00:08:16.670
Sir,

00:08:16.870 --> 00:08:18.240
I kindly remind you.

00:08:18.560 --> 00:08:20.240
The name you know might be fake too.

00:08:20.240 --> 00:08:21.560
- Miss Chen, is it?
- Don't be fooled by her.

00:08:22.630 --> 00:08:23.480
I remember now.

00:08:25.750 --> 00:08:27.600
I never thought you'd still put up with him.

00:08:28.480 --> 00:08:30.040
I just wonder... has your husband finished

00:08:30.390 --> 00:08:31.480
with his other woman?

00:08:31.480 --> 00:08:32.440
Shut up.

00:08:32.440 --> 00:08:33.280
What now?

00:08:35.360 --> 00:08:36.360
For a moment,

00:08:36.360 --> 00:08:38.080
I saw who I used to be.

00:08:39.320 --> 00:08:40.160
I understand you.

00:08:40.720 --> 00:08:41.790
So I don't blame you.

00:08:43.790 --> 00:08:45.480
You two met in an elevator too?

00:08:45.870 --> 00:08:46.710
Oh, by the way,

00:08:49.080 --> 00:08:50.240
how did she seduce you?

00:08:50.480 --> 00:08:51.320
Watch your language.

00:08:51.320 --> 00:08:52.240
Sir,

00:08:52.240 --> 00:08:53.600
please don't defend her.

00:08:53.750 --> 00:08:54.960
Don't you know how many

00:08:54.960 --> 00:08:56.000
dirty things she's done?

00:08:56.240 --> 00:08:57.510
Keep your messy affairs

00:08:57.510 --> 00:08:58.910
to yourselves.

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:01.030
Throwing mud at others...

00:09:01.360 --> 00:09:02.630
Feeling proud, huh?

00:09:03.480 --> 00:09:05.910
If everything comes out, you know well

00:09:06.550 --> 00:09:07.840
who's dirty.

00:09:11.910 --> 00:09:13.240
Hooking up with two at once?

00:09:15.390 --> 00:09:16.910
Your game's improved.

00:09:18.630 --> 00:09:20.240
That's nonsense. Apologize to her.

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:21.720
- Why?
- Apologize!

00:09:22.390 --> 00:09:23.600
- Bei, let him go.
- Did you hear me?

00:09:23.600 --> 00:09:24.440
Bei, just let it go.

00:09:24.440 --> 00:09:25.720
Didn't you hear me? Apologize.

00:09:26.120 --> 00:09:26.960
Mr. Bei.

00:09:30.360 --> 00:09:31.200
Buddy,

00:09:32.030 --> 00:09:34.030
looks like she's your inevitable curse.

00:09:51.240 --> 00:09:52.080
Are you okay?

00:10:00.150 --> 00:10:00.990
I'm cold too.

00:10:01.270 --> 00:10:02.110
Go away.

00:10:14.670 --> 00:10:16.240
You were too worked up earlier.

00:10:18.630 --> 00:10:19.510
From now on,

00:10:20.360 --> 00:10:21.630
you can tell me everything.

00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:23.360
No need to hide anything.

00:10:25.790 --> 00:10:26.910
Emotional dumping on you?

00:10:29.120 --> 00:10:30.120
Do you think hiding it

00:10:31.080 --> 00:10:32.150
was for my sake,

00:10:32.390 --> 00:10:33.390
or yours?

00:10:37.480 --> 00:10:38.320
Honestly,

00:10:41.030 --> 00:10:42.270
I did this for you,

00:10:42.750 --> 00:10:43.590
for her,

00:10:44.120 --> 00:10:44.960
and for everyone.

00:10:49.390 --> 00:10:50.240
Then why did you

00:10:50.240 --> 00:10:51.360
bring up Jiang Yifan

00:10:51.360 --> 00:10:52.360
the first time

00:10:53.000 --> 00:10:54.240
I introduced Li Xiaoxi to you?

00:10:54.240 --> 00:10:55.240
(You fall in love)

00:10:55.240 --> 00:10:57.670
(not because she's beautiful or tall,)

00:10:57.670 --> 00:10:59.630
(but because the sun was shining,)

00:11:00.320 --> 00:11:01.200
(the breeze was gentle,)

00:11:02.000 --> 00:11:03.630
(and she happened to be smiling.)

00:11:04.150 --> 00:11:05.510
Jiang Yifan is Jiang Yifan.

00:11:06.080 --> 00:11:07.870
Jiang Yifan will never be Li Xiaoxi.

00:11:08.150 --> 00:11:10.200
I guess I only loved a fictional character.

00:11:18.080 --> 00:11:18.920
I was planning to

00:11:19.080 --> 00:11:20.790
share some good news at dinner.

00:11:22.320 --> 00:11:23.160
Li Xiaoxi

00:11:23.440 --> 00:11:24.550
accepted my proposal.

00:11:28.360 --> 00:11:29.390
I knew it.

00:11:30.000 --> 00:11:32.240
I've never seen anyone turn down a proposal.

00:11:32.510 --> 00:11:33.350
Congratulations.

00:11:34.200 --> 00:11:35.200
From now on...

00:11:35.200 --> 00:11:36.600
"From now on, take good care of her."

00:11:36.840 --> 00:11:37.840
"Or I won't let you off."

00:11:39.200 --> 00:11:40.840
Are you gonna say something that cheesy?

00:11:50.660 --> 00:11:54.540
(Delusional Girl)

00:11:54.550 --> 00:11:55.390
Thanks.

00:11:57.960 --> 00:11:59.270
What kept you so long?

00:12:00.480 --> 00:12:01.670
Mr. Bei has this problem.

00:12:02.480 --> 00:12:03.390
That's exactly you.

00:12:05.390 --> 00:12:06.440
See you around, Yu He.

00:12:06.440 --> 00:12:07.280
Let's do lunch sometime.

00:12:07.670 --> 00:12:08.510
Sure.

00:12:09.320 --> 00:12:10.160
Bye.

00:12:11.390 --> 00:12:13.080
Why didn't you offer to treat me?

00:12:13.720 --> 00:12:14.750
You don't deserve it.

00:12:24.440 --> 00:12:25.280
Let's go.

00:12:27.240 --> 00:12:28.080
Yeah.

00:12:28.900 --> 00:12:30.660
(Salted Pineapple)

00:12:32.960 --> 00:12:33.870
You didn't drive?

00:12:34.270 --> 00:12:35.550
It's late. I'll call a cab for you.

00:12:35.550 --> 00:12:36.390
I drove.

00:12:37.600 --> 00:12:38.440
Want a ride?

00:12:40.960 --> 00:12:41.800
Is it on your way?

00:12:42.240 --> 00:12:43.260
- My place is...
- Yes.

00:12:44.550 --> 00:12:45.720
I haven't said where I live.

00:12:47.200 --> 00:12:48.040
Are you coming or not?

00:12:54.550 --> 00:12:55.390
Yeah.

00:12:59.150 --> 00:12:59.990
This way.

00:13:09.440 --> 00:13:11.600
Are you worried about Mingming and Sen?

00:13:13.550 --> 00:13:14.390
Yeah.

00:13:15.720 --> 00:13:17.510
When Sen was pursuing Mingming,

00:13:18.240 --> 00:13:19.870
I thought she was just flirting with that guy.

00:13:20.630 --> 00:13:22.270
I didn't know he was married.

00:13:25.480 --> 00:13:27.200
She might've been tricked.

00:13:28.030 --> 00:13:29.080
No one checks someone's ID

00:13:29.080 --> 00:13:30.390
before falling in love.

00:13:31.150 --> 00:13:32.840
But nobody really cares about the truth.

00:13:34.840 --> 00:13:36.510
I'm worried about how Mingming

00:13:36.870 --> 00:13:38.080
is holding up.

00:13:38.670 --> 00:13:39.510
And Sen.

00:13:40.270 --> 00:13:41.320
From what I know about him,

00:13:42.000 --> 00:13:43.270
he's probably falling apart.

00:13:44.080 --> 00:13:45.670
Will he break up with Mingming?

00:13:48.200 --> 00:13:49.040
No idea.

00:13:53.030 --> 00:13:54.240
I'm more worried about Mingming.

00:13:56.240 --> 00:13:57.630
I hope she gets through this soon.

00:13:57.630 --> 00:13:58.910
This whole thing is a nightmare.

00:14:00.380 --> 00:14:02.460
That's not the only nightmare today.

00:14:03.670 --> 00:14:05.390
I wonder what Yu thought of the play.

00:14:06.510 --> 00:14:08.360
Luanluan's perspective was too unfair to Yu.

00:14:12.960 --> 00:14:15.150
After watching it, I think Xiu is selfish.

00:14:16.030 --> 00:14:17.840
He doesn't get Yu's pain at all.

00:14:20.620 --> 00:14:22.320
I wonder how they're doing now.

00:14:24.030 --> 00:14:25.510
To celebrate our dear Luanluan,

00:14:25.510 --> 00:14:29.200
for her first self-written play,

00:14:29.910 --> 00:14:31.390
Delusion Girl. What do you say?

00:14:32.080 --> 00:14:33.600
- A hit!
- The debut was amazing!

00:14:33.600 --> 00:14:35.480
- Total success!
- Thank you!

00:14:37.790 --> 00:14:38.750
Bottoms up! Chug it!

00:14:41.630 --> 00:14:42.720
I'd like to make a toast.

00:14:44.030 --> 00:14:45.150
I really appreciate you guys.

00:14:45.480 --> 00:14:48.080
Let's eat and drink our fill tonight.

00:14:48.550 --> 00:14:49.480
My treat. Go nuts!

00:14:49.480 --> 00:14:50.790
Drink the night away, guys!

00:14:51.030 --> 00:14:52.600
- Sure!
- Absolutely!

00:14:52.760 --> 00:14:53.600
Waiter!

00:14:53.600 --> 00:14:55.120
A case of beer, waiter!

00:14:55.290 --> 00:14:56.150
Alright, that's enough.

00:14:56.150 --> 00:14:57.000
Let's eat first.

00:14:57.000 --> 00:14:57.840
Yeah, dig in.

00:14:58.000 --> 00:14:59.790
Your bowl's empty. Have some fish.

00:15:02.270 --> 00:15:03.480
Why don't you serve me?

00:15:06.200 --> 00:15:07.040
Come on.

00:15:07.630 --> 00:15:10.750
She's our troupe's Juliet.

00:15:10.980 --> 00:15:11.840
Juliet?

00:15:11.840 --> 00:15:12.870
Then I'm Ophelia.

00:15:12.870 --> 00:15:14.600
Ophelia? Then I'm Polonius.

00:15:14.600 --> 00:15:16.080
Fine, then I'll be Mona Lisa.

00:15:16.320 --> 00:15:17.720
Hold on. One question for you.

00:15:18.000 --> 00:15:19.120
Who forgot their lines on stage?

00:15:19.120 --> 00:15:21.080
That must be him!

00:15:21.080 --> 00:15:22.270
That was you, Henry?

00:15:22.270 --> 00:15:23.630
I didn't forget the lines.

00:15:23.790 --> 00:15:25.910
That pause was on purpose.

00:15:25.910 --> 00:15:27.120
For dramatic effect.

00:15:27.120 --> 00:15:28.270
Exactly, dramatic effect.

00:15:28.270 --> 00:15:29.670
- A pause?
- Stop making excuses.

00:15:29.840 --> 00:15:31.120
- You owe us a drink.
- Pay the penalty!

00:15:31.320 --> 00:15:32.160
I can drink,

00:15:32.170 --> 00:15:33.630
but everyone's joining,

00:15:33.630 --> 00:15:34.510
or it counts as a penalty.

00:15:34.510 --> 00:15:35.790
Come on, drink up.

00:15:35.790 --> 00:15:37.150
- Just one glass.
- Bottom up!

00:15:37.150 --> 00:15:39.390
Come on! All of us!

00:15:40.170 --> 00:15:41.030
Cheers!

00:15:41.030 --> 00:15:43.120
Take it easy. You've had a lot.

00:15:43.120 --> 00:15:43.960
Luanluan.

00:15:46.480 --> 00:15:49.600
Let me be real with you.

00:15:49.600 --> 00:15:50.750
It's not the drinks talking.

00:15:51.270 --> 00:15:52.790
I feel like you've been

00:15:53.270 --> 00:15:54.480
unhappy deep down.

00:15:55.750 --> 00:15:56.590
Seriously.

00:15:57.150 --> 00:15:58.910
If there's something

00:15:58.910 --> 00:16:00.320
you can't tell anyone else,

00:16:00.320 --> 00:16:01.790
you can tell me, okay?

00:16:01.800 --> 00:16:02.650
You're drunk.

00:16:02.650 --> 00:16:04.270
I'm not, really.

00:16:04.600 --> 00:16:06.750
Don't be unhappy. Talk to me.

00:16:07.240 --> 00:16:08.080
Need to use the restroom.

00:16:08.080 --> 00:16:08.920
You…

00:16:09.360 --> 00:16:10.200
Keep it low-key.

00:16:10.630 --> 00:16:11.960
Any tips getting rid of neck lines?

00:16:14.790 --> 00:16:15.840
Just don't crack up out there.

00:16:16.000 --> 00:16:17.120
Don't follow those two,

00:16:17.320 --> 00:16:18.160
you know?

00:16:18.280 --> 00:16:19.120
Bro, cheers.

00:16:19.120 --> 00:16:20.360
Thanks for saving us tonight.

00:16:20.360 --> 00:16:21.200
Yeah, totally.

00:16:21.550 --> 00:16:23.600
Seriously, I didn't forget the lines.

00:16:23.910 --> 00:16:24.750
What's wrong?

00:16:26.440 --> 00:16:27.360
You guys go ahead.

00:16:27.360 --> 00:16:28.510
- Sure.
- Drink up.

00:16:28.510 --> 00:16:29.600
I'm going to the restroom.

00:16:29.870 --> 00:16:30.790
I'll check on Luanluan.

00:16:31.200 --> 00:16:32.040
She might be drunk.

00:16:34.630 --> 00:16:37.030
Don't "oh" me! Let me fill you up.

00:16:37.030 --> 00:16:38.270
Pour up, everyone!

00:16:39.030 --> 00:16:40.440
- Go on.
- Make it quick.

00:16:40.440 --> 00:16:41.840
Sure, I'll be right back.

00:16:41.840 --> 00:16:42.710
Don't try to bail on us.

00:16:42.710 --> 00:16:43.600
Never.

00:16:43.600 --> 00:16:51.500
(Qian Chang Photography Studio)

00:16:54.380 --> 00:16:55.270
(Since you're here,)

00:16:55.270 --> 00:16:56.550
(do you want to take a photo?)

00:16:56.550 --> 00:16:57.840
(Three, two, one.)

00:17:17.270 --> 00:17:18.110
Yu?

00:17:19.310 --> 00:17:20.510
Come home with me, okay?

00:17:20.780 --> 00:17:21.640
Come on.

00:17:21.640 --> 00:17:22.480
Don't touch me.

00:17:25.640 --> 00:17:27.030
Go back to your little lover.

00:17:30.200 --> 00:17:31.200
Look at you two,

00:17:32.750 --> 00:17:33.880
all cozy and intimate.

00:17:35.160 --> 00:17:36.270
Such a perfect match.

00:17:38.480 --> 00:17:39.590
What do you want?

00:17:41.270 --> 00:17:43.000
Announcing it to the world?

00:17:43.160 --> 00:17:44.200
I've broken up with her.

00:17:44.510 --> 00:17:45.350
It's true.

00:17:45.960 --> 00:17:47.030
You disgust me.

00:17:48.920 --> 00:17:50.160
I was so stupid.

00:17:51.510 --> 00:17:53.160
I actually knew it all along.

00:17:54.680 --> 00:17:56.400
I pretended not to know anything.

00:17:56.400 --> 00:17:58.720
I thought we could start over that way.

00:17:58.720 --> 00:17:59.720
And then?

00:18:02.480 --> 00:18:03.320
It's true.

00:18:04.510 --> 00:18:05.440
I... I'm not lying to you.

00:18:05.880 --> 00:18:07.000
I did break up with her.

00:18:07.270 --> 00:18:08.270
Seeing the play should be

00:18:08.270 --> 00:18:09.110
the last time I...

00:18:09.130 --> 00:18:10.550
You dare bring up the play?

00:18:11.680 --> 00:18:13.160
What did I ever do wrong?

00:18:13.920 --> 00:18:15.160
Why do you treat me like this?

00:18:17.640 --> 00:18:19.240
Talking behind my back

00:18:19.240 --> 00:18:21.440
with your little lover wasn't enough.

00:18:21.440 --> 00:18:22.790
You had to

00:18:24.110 --> 00:18:26.350
humiliate me right on stage too!

00:18:26.510 --> 00:18:27.720
I didn't know the script.

00:18:27.720 --> 00:18:28.590
I really didn't.

00:18:28.720 --> 00:18:29.680
I swear, I didn't.

00:18:29.680 --> 00:18:31.310
Oh sure, you're the innocent one.

00:18:31.880 --> 00:18:33.510
You didn't tell her those

00:18:34.070 --> 00:18:35.070
awesome stories,

00:18:36.240 --> 00:18:37.440
but I did?

00:18:46.310 --> 00:18:47.150
Hey, Luanluan.

00:18:52.640 --> 00:18:53.480
What's wrong?

00:18:58.310 --> 00:18:59.150
Luanluan,

00:19:00.200 --> 00:19:01.040
I like you.

00:19:01.480 --> 00:19:03.270
Will you be my girlfriend?

00:19:03.420 --> 00:19:04.270
What?

00:19:04.270 --> 00:19:06.160
Wait, you don't have to answer now.

00:19:06.160 --> 00:19:07.000
Just think about it.

00:19:07.550 --> 00:19:09.110
Did you forget I have a boyfriend?

00:19:09.400 --> 00:19:10.440
I'm sorry, Hao.

00:19:15.200 --> 00:19:16.200
I overheard everything

00:19:16.790 --> 00:19:17.630
backstage today.

00:19:18.000 --> 00:19:19.270
Nothing really happened

00:19:19.270 --> 00:19:20.790
between Xiu and me.

00:19:21.400 --> 00:19:23.830
Are you saying your relationship was pure

00:19:24.110 --> 00:19:24.950
and noble?

00:19:25.830 --> 00:19:26.960
I don't buy it.

00:19:28.070 --> 00:19:29.070
Men cheat for nothing

00:19:29.070 --> 00:19:31.240
more than a temporary thrill.

00:19:32.200 --> 00:19:33.640
You're young now,

00:19:34.270 --> 00:19:35.790
but you're a fleeting thrill for him.

00:19:37.790 --> 00:19:38.630
Last time,

00:19:39.750 --> 00:19:41.550
that creepy guy who popped up out of nowhere

00:19:42.270 --> 00:19:43.880
was your so-called boyfriend?

00:19:44.590 --> 00:19:46.030
Still, I didn't expect this.

00:19:48.200 --> 00:19:49.070
How do you

00:19:50.110 --> 00:19:51.200
get around so much?

00:19:52.920 --> 00:19:53.760
Let go of me.

00:19:54.920 --> 00:19:56.480
We're both actors.

00:19:56.680 --> 00:19:57.550
We're old friends.

00:19:57.550 --> 00:19:58.960
You can drop the act.

00:19:59.160 --> 00:20:01.240
Let's talk outside, alright?

00:20:03.440 --> 00:20:04.400
No, I just...

00:20:04.400 --> 00:20:05.680
- Just a few words.
- Stop it!

00:20:05.680 --> 00:20:07.200
Yeah, I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

00:20:07.200 --> 00:20:08.400
I got carried away.

00:20:08.680 --> 00:20:09.750
But I mean it.

00:20:09.750 --> 00:20:11.160
I truly like you.

00:20:11.160 --> 00:20:12.640
Can we please talk outside?

00:20:12.640 --> 00:20:13.960
Get out of here and talk calmly.

00:20:14.110 --> 00:20:14.950
Don't do this here.

00:20:15.160 --> 00:20:16.440
Move. Let me out.

00:20:21.270 --> 00:20:22.110
Or do you

00:20:22.640 --> 00:20:23.590
like it exciting?

00:20:23.590 --> 00:20:25.310
Are you out of your mind?

00:20:25.310 --> 00:20:26.270
I'm fine with it.

00:20:26.270 --> 00:20:27.110
Totally fine.

00:20:28.640 --> 00:20:29.680
Let go!

00:20:29.920 --> 00:20:31.750
I'm totally fine with that, Luanluan.

00:20:32.030 --> 00:20:32.880
Juliet.

00:20:35.880 --> 00:20:36.920
- Let go.
- So that's it?

00:20:36.920 --> 00:20:37.960
You enjoy it this way, huh?

00:20:42.900 --> 00:20:44.580
(Restroom)

00:21:18.620 --> 00:21:21.820
(Luanluan)

00:21:23.680 --> 00:21:24.520
Why did you hang up?

00:21:28.310 --> 00:21:29.150
Call her back.

00:21:29.920 --> 00:21:30.760
I'm begging you.

00:21:31.310 --> 00:21:32.550
Please don't do this.

00:21:33.160 --> 00:21:34.400
I want to know what she wants.

00:21:35.350 --> 00:21:36.880
So eager, isn't she?

00:21:37.960 --> 00:21:38.800
She and I

00:21:39.880 --> 00:21:41.440
are really over.

00:21:41.680 --> 00:21:43.160
Can you be reasonable, honey?

00:21:43.590 --> 00:21:45.240
So I'm the unreasonable one again?

00:21:47.160 --> 00:21:48.880
Did you hear me? Call her back.

00:21:51.160 --> 00:21:52.070
You're not calling?

00:21:53.270 --> 00:21:54.110
Fine,

00:21:54.790 --> 00:21:56.510
I'll go to my parents

00:21:56.750 --> 00:21:57.920
and your parents.

00:21:57.920 --> 00:21:59.270
I'll tell them everything

00:21:59.270 --> 00:22:00.960
you've done all these years!

00:22:01.480 --> 00:22:02.440
I'll call her back.

00:22:11.590 --> 00:22:12.550
Put it on speaker.

00:22:18.310 --> 00:22:19.310
Xiu.

00:22:19.590 --> 00:22:21.240
- We already broke up.
- Just now...

00:22:21.240 --> 00:22:22.590
That day, we agreed, didn't we?

00:22:23.110 --> 00:22:24.520
Hello? Say something!

00:22:24.960 --> 00:22:25.880
After the play,

00:22:25.880 --> 00:22:26.830
we were done for good.

00:22:27.240 --> 00:22:28.270
You... Talk to me.

00:22:28.270 --> 00:22:29.110
Hello?

00:22:29.240 --> 00:22:30.440
Dropping your act now, huh?

00:22:31.750 --> 00:22:33.590
You were great on stage.

00:22:34.070 --> 00:22:35.880
You even asked me if I plead guilty.

00:22:36.590 --> 00:22:38.960
You know what? Have some basic decency.

00:22:38.960 --> 00:22:40.440
You put someone's private life on stage.

00:22:40.440 --> 00:22:41.280
What do you want?

00:22:41.680 --> 00:22:42.720
You want everyone to see

00:22:42.720 --> 00:22:44.790
how pathetic Xiu is to have a wife like me?

00:22:45.240 --> 00:22:46.160
And you're

00:22:46.400 --> 00:22:48.920
his perfect, sweet, sensible partner?

00:22:49.350 --> 00:22:51.310
You want everyone to pity you two,

00:22:51.310 --> 00:22:52.680
star-crossed lovers, don't you?

00:22:54.480 --> 00:22:56.440
Aren't you tired of sneaking around?

00:22:57.070 --> 00:22:58.750
I feel exhausted for both of you!

00:22:59.960 --> 00:23:01.030
Listen.

00:23:02.310 --> 00:23:03.480
I'm done with this man.

00:23:04.310 --> 00:23:06.160
You can be together every single day.

00:23:06.640 --> 00:23:07.720
Write songs together.

00:23:08.920 --> 00:23:09.960
Make art every day.

00:23:11.110 --> 00:23:12.590
Do whatever you want!

00:23:14.720 --> 00:23:15.790
Do you have parents?

00:23:15.920 --> 00:23:17.640
Do they know their daughter

00:23:17.640 --> 00:23:19.030
is fooling around

00:23:19.310 --> 00:23:20.240
with a married man?

00:23:20.240 --> 00:23:21.200
That's enough!

00:23:21.200 --> 00:23:22.920
I told you we're done!

00:23:23.070 --> 00:23:24.640
If you've got a problem, take it out on me!

00:23:28.720 --> 00:23:30.350
It's very chivalrous of you to defend her.

00:23:36.240 --> 00:23:37.640
When she humiliated me on stage,

00:23:37.640 --> 00:23:38.720
what were you doing?

00:23:44.680 --> 00:23:46.440
Applauding in your head?

00:24:27.950 --> 00:24:28.830
You brat.

00:24:28.830 --> 00:24:30.160
Why didn't you answer my calls?

00:24:30.160 --> 00:24:31.590
I was worried about you.

00:24:34.270 --> 00:24:35.310
What's wrong, Luanluan?

00:24:35.480 --> 00:24:36.320
What happened?

00:24:38.590 --> 00:24:39.430
Did someone upset you?

00:24:40.000 --> 00:24:40.880
Was it that guy?

00:24:42.550 --> 00:24:44.680
I told you he wasn't reliable.

00:24:44.960 --> 00:24:46.680
You should've broken up sooner.

00:24:47.720 --> 00:24:49.270
Mr. Zhang's son is a great young man.

00:24:49.270 --> 00:24:50.160
He likes you a lot

00:24:50.160 --> 00:24:51.270
and came to see your play.

00:24:51.440 --> 00:24:52.720
He's asked you out but you refused.

00:24:52.740 --> 00:24:53.580
I'll set it up tomorrow.

00:24:53.580 --> 00:24:54.590
You have to go.

00:24:56.270 --> 00:24:57.310
I'm doing fine.

00:24:57.680 --> 00:24:59.240
Fine? You're crouched here crying!

00:25:00.240 --> 00:25:01.080
How's that fine?

00:25:02.350 --> 00:25:03.960
Mr. Zhang's son is a good catch.

00:25:04.680 --> 00:25:05.550
His family's well-off.

00:25:05.550 --> 00:25:07.110
If you were with him,

00:25:07.110 --> 00:25:08.240
I'd be at ease

00:25:08.240 --> 00:25:09.590
and you'd be happy, right?

00:25:17.550 --> 00:25:19.030
I've got something to take care of.

00:25:19.880 --> 00:25:21.550
Don't worry. We're fully prepared.

00:25:21.550 --> 00:25:22.830
We'll secure that project.

00:25:23.790 --> 00:25:24.830
Okay. Okay.

00:25:25.240 --> 00:25:26.270
I'll call you back later.

00:25:27.440 --> 00:25:28.510
I'm not lecturing you.

00:25:28.880 --> 00:25:30.750
Dad knows what marriage is like.

00:25:30.750 --> 00:25:31.640
You should listen to me

00:25:31.640 --> 00:25:33.240
about choosing a boyfriend, okay?

00:25:33.240 --> 00:25:34.880
Who I date is none of your business.

00:25:34.890 --> 00:25:35.760
I'm your father.

00:25:35.760 --> 00:25:37.070
Of course it's my business.

00:25:37.550 --> 00:25:38.920
Now you remember you're my father?

00:25:43.000 --> 00:25:44.000
From childhood till now,

00:25:44.640 --> 00:25:45.640
what have you ever cared about?

00:25:48.900 --> 00:25:50.420
(Manager Wang)

00:25:51.920 --> 00:25:53.030
I never cared about you?

00:25:53.830 --> 00:25:55.510
Then how did you grow up like this?

00:25:55.920 --> 00:25:57.680
I worked hard to pay for your food,

00:25:57.680 --> 00:25:59.480
your clothes, everything you need.

00:26:01.310 --> 00:26:02.150
Alright, alright.

00:26:02.790 --> 00:26:03.720
Luanluan.

00:26:03.720 --> 00:26:04.750
Don't be mad at Dad.

00:26:05.440 --> 00:26:06.680
Let's grab a bite.

00:26:08.160 --> 00:26:09.790
I'll take you for that Italian place.

00:26:09.790 --> 00:26:10.880
Your favorite...

00:26:11.080 --> 00:26:11.920
carpaccio,

00:26:11.920 --> 00:26:13.000
and lasagna.

00:26:13.240 --> 00:26:14.080
- Okay?
- No need.

00:26:14.980 --> 00:26:16.180
(Manager Wang)

00:26:18.680 --> 00:26:20.310
Just answer it.

00:26:26.310 --> 00:26:27.550
Hello? I know.

00:26:27.550 --> 00:26:29.200
Mr. Jiang is there. Go chat with him.

00:26:29.510 --> 00:26:30.680
Okay? It's a private matter.

00:26:30.680 --> 00:26:31.520
I'll be there soon.

00:26:31.750 --> 00:26:32.590
Yeah.

00:26:32.960 --> 00:26:34.000
Yeah, drink my wine.

00:26:34.310 --> 00:26:35.150
I've got it.

00:26:35.480 --> 00:26:36.510
Yeah, it's in the trunk.

00:26:37.350 --> 00:26:38.270
I talked to him.

00:26:38.270 --> 00:26:39.640
We can't lose this project,

00:26:39.650 --> 00:26:40.510
right?

00:26:40.510 --> 00:26:41.640
Alright, alright.

00:26:41.640 --> 00:26:42.920
Get the message across. Okay.

00:26:43.160 --> 00:26:44.000
Luan...

00:26:45.400 --> 00:26:46.240
Luanluan?

00:26:46.920 --> 00:26:47.760
Luanluan?

00:26:52.530 --> 00:26:53.400
Here we are.

00:26:53.400 --> 00:26:54.240
Yeah.

00:26:59.880 --> 00:27:01.720
Someone's bought the rights to my comic.

00:27:02.920 --> 00:27:04.680
I'm meeting the director in a few days.

00:27:09.750 --> 00:27:11.000
You're the first person I told.

00:27:12.880 --> 00:27:13.720
No congratulations?

00:27:17.400 --> 00:27:18.240
Congratulations.

00:27:21.070 --> 00:27:21.910
Thanks.

00:27:27.160 --> 00:27:28.000
Drive safe.

00:27:38.200 --> 00:27:39.400
Shouldn't we celebrate

00:27:40.070 --> 00:27:41.070
with a drink?

00:27:44.720 --> 00:27:45.560
Good idea.

00:27:48.960 --> 00:27:49.800
You coming over?

00:27:59.720 --> 00:28:00.560
Stop scrolling.

00:28:01.880 --> 00:28:03.030
Just bored people online.

00:28:03.820 --> 00:28:05.420
(Power off)

00:28:05.420 --> 00:28:06.300
(Tap to power off)

00:28:08.680 --> 00:28:10.070
Have some water. Here.

00:28:22.590 --> 00:28:23.430
Who is it?

00:28:24.000 --> 00:28:24.840
Food delivery.

00:28:36.920 --> 00:28:38.880
Hello, this is the cake you ordered.

00:28:38.880 --> 00:28:40.000
One "Eros's Wish".

00:28:53.720 --> 00:28:54.680
It's Eros's Wish,

00:28:56.350 --> 00:28:57.590
from that Dark Magic bakery.

00:29:00.030 --> 00:29:01.310
Legend says this cake is

00:29:01.310 --> 00:29:03.310
as intoxicating as the strongest love potion.

00:29:03.640 --> 00:29:06.110
Those who share it will fall madly in love

00:29:06.400 --> 00:29:08.720
and stay together until their last breath.

00:29:10.550 --> 00:29:11.390
Let's skip it.

00:29:11.880 --> 00:29:12.720
No.

00:29:14.510 --> 00:29:15.350
I insist.

00:29:16.790 --> 00:29:17.960
At least one bite.

00:29:32.500 --> 00:29:33.980
(Cousin)

00:29:34.350 --> 00:29:35.190
My cousin.

00:29:37.110 --> 00:29:38.000
I'll take this.

00:29:55.750 --> 00:29:57.070
Hello?

00:29:59.200 --> 00:30:00.200
Oh, my dear cousin.

00:30:00.790 --> 00:30:01.960
I'm begging you, can you

00:30:01.960 --> 00:30:03.350
not cause me any trouble?

00:30:03.350 --> 00:30:05.310
I'm already overwhelmed.

00:30:08.350 --> 00:30:09.190
Oh no!

00:30:09.510 --> 00:30:11.680
It's not what you think.

00:30:13.350 --> 00:30:15.160
Did Aunt have nothing better to do?

00:30:15.750 --> 00:30:17.110
Why did she send that to my mom?

00:30:48.400 --> 00:30:50.240
Just pretend you know nothing.

00:30:50.240 --> 00:30:51.110
Say you don't know.

00:30:51.110 --> 00:30:52.510
Don't say anything else to them,

00:30:52.510 --> 00:30:53.350
okay?

00:30:55.750 --> 00:30:56.750
Yeah, relax.

00:30:56.750 --> 00:30:57.590
Don't worry.

00:30:58.070 --> 00:30:58.920
I won't act rashly.

00:30:58.920 --> 00:30:59.880
Yeah, I won't.

00:31:03.240 --> 00:31:04.160
Who is it?

00:31:08.590 --> 00:31:09.550
I'm sorry.

00:31:09.550 --> 00:31:10.390
Let go of me.

00:31:10.680 --> 00:31:11.920
- I'm sorry.
- Let go!

00:31:11.920 --> 00:31:13.200
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

00:31:15.070 --> 00:31:16.200
How dare you touch her?

00:31:16.200 --> 00:31:17.400
Do you have a death wish?

00:31:17.400 --> 00:31:18.270
No!

00:31:18.270 --> 00:31:19.160
Stop hitting him!

00:31:19.160 --> 00:31:20.550
Please stop, Sen!

00:31:20.680 --> 00:31:21.920
I'm sorry, I mean it. I just...

00:31:21.920 --> 00:31:23.270
Look what you did to her!

00:31:23.400 --> 00:31:24.590
Are you trying to kill her?

00:31:24.590 --> 00:31:25.640
Let go!

00:31:25.640 --> 00:31:26.720
- What are you doing?
- Sorry...

00:31:27.550 --> 00:31:28.390
Why are you here?

00:31:29.020 --> 00:31:29.870
Hui.

00:31:29.880 --> 00:31:30.920
Go home, Hui!

00:31:30.970 --> 00:31:31.830
Hui!

00:31:31.830 --> 00:31:32.790
Hui! Hui! Hui!

00:31:32.790 --> 00:31:34.110
You seduced my husband!

00:31:34.110 --> 00:31:35.590
- Are you crazy?
- Shameless homewrecker!

00:31:35.590 --> 00:31:36.430
Are you okay?

00:31:37.070 --> 00:31:38.350
You posted those photos, didn't you?

00:31:38.350 --> 00:31:39.480
Yeah, I did. So what?

00:31:39.700 --> 00:31:40.590
You stole my husband

00:31:40.590 --> 00:31:42.200
and yet you're scared of exposure?

00:31:43.070 --> 00:31:44.200
You must be her boyfriend.

00:31:44.440 --> 00:31:45.400
You'll get cheated on!

00:31:45.400 --> 00:31:46.830
Watch your mouth!

00:31:47.030 --> 00:31:48.720
You should leash your dirty dog!

00:31:49.070 --> 00:31:50.550
Listen, karma is real.

00:31:50.680 --> 00:31:52.400
Don't let your child pay for your sins.

00:31:52.400 --> 00:31:53.270
You dare say that again?

00:31:53.270 --> 00:31:54.350
Sure. What are you gonna do?

00:31:58.940 --> 00:31:59.790
Stop it!

00:31:59.790 --> 00:32:01.000
Stop it! Stop!

00:32:02.070 --> 00:32:03.110
Stop!

00:32:11.550 --> 00:32:13.440
Sen, I'm begging you. Stop!

00:32:13.440 --> 00:32:14.920
Let them go.

00:32:28.480 --> 00:32:29.830
Hui! Hui!

00:32:30.110 --> 00:32:31.160
Are you okay?

00:32:31.310 --> 00:32:32.400
How are you feeling?

00:32:32.400 --> 00:32:33.440
It feels like...

00:32:33.880 --> 00:32:34.830
my water broke.

00:32:34.830 --> 00:32:36.030
Get her to the hospital! Now!

00:32:36.030 --> 00:32:37.240
Get her to the hospital!

00:32:37.680 --> 00:32:38.550
Hui!

00:32:38.550 --> 00:32:40.160
Your arm. Here, let me help you up.

00:32:40.160 --> 00:32:41.160
Easy, take it slow.

00:32:41.160 --> 00:32:42.200
Alright. One, two.

00:32:46.880 --> 00:32:48.270
Hui. Hui.

00:32:48.510 --> 00:32:49.510
How are you feeling?

00:32:50.310 --> 00:32:51.160
Don't worry, I'm here.

00:32:51.400 --> 00:32:52.400
I'm right here.

00:32:52.680 --> 00:32:53.680
How's it feel?

00:32:55.240 --> 00:32:56.200
It comes in waves.

00:32:56.750 --> 00:32:57.590
Feels like...

00:32:57.880 --> 00:32:58.830
contractions.

00:32:58.830 --> 00:32:59.720
Contractions?

00:32:59.720 --> 00:33:01.030
Sharp pain?

00:33:01.240 --> 00:33:02.440
Does it feel like...

00:33:02.440 --> 00:33:03.640
Don't let her talk now.

00:33:03.920 --> 00:33:04.960
Save her strength.

00:33:07.400 --> 00:33:08.310
Have some rest.

00:33:08.310 --> 00:33:09.880
Hang on. We're almost there.

00:33:10.070 --> 00:33:10.910
Hang in there.

00:33:13.880 --> 00:33:14.960
Thanks, man.

00:33:15.270 --> 00:33:16.240
No need to thank me.

00:33:16.640 --> 00:33:17.790
If you really want to,

00:33:17.790 --> 00:33:19.070
delete that post ASAP.

00:33:19.440 --> 00:33:20.750
Handle your own mess.

00:33:21.270 --> 00:33:22.550
Stop dragging my girlfriend into it.

00:33:23.400 --> 00:33:24.240
Alright.

00:33:25.030 --> 00:33:25.870
Hui.

00:33:26.030 --> 00:33:26.870
Hui, hey!

00:33:27.590 --> 00:33:28.430
Hang in there.

00:33:29.160 --> 00:33:30.880
I'm right here. I'm right here.

00:33:33.480 --> 00:33:34.320
Okay.

00:33:34.510 --> 00:33:36.270
Take a deep breath with me.

00:33:36.270 --> 00:33:37.680
Follow my lead. Breathe in.

00:33:54.110 --> 00:33:55.750
- Good, keep going!
- One more!

00:33:55.750 --> 00:33:57.070
Take another deep breath.

00:33:57.070 --> 00:33:58.510
Ready? One, two,

00:33:58.790 --> 00:33:59.630
three!

00:34:02.310 --> 00:34:04.510
Good. Great.

00:34:07.200 --> 00:34:08.360
You've got this.

00:34:11.630 --> 00:34:12.710
It's all my fault.

00:34:12.710 --> 00:34:14.440
Hui, you can do this.

00:34:15.030 --> 00:34:15.880
Three!

00:34:18.840 --> 00:34:20.480
Good. Keep doing!

00:34:20.480 --> 00:34:21.400
You've got this.

00:34:21.760 --> 00:34:22.600
Hui.

00:34:22.600 --> 00:34:25.500
(Delivery Room)

00:34:39.150 --> 00:34:40.360
Luckily, you were there.

00:34:42.280 --> 00:34:43.120
Otherwise,

00:34:43.360 --> 00:34:44.480
I'd have panicked.

00:34:44.480 --> 00:34:45.630
I had no idea what to do.

00:34:46.400 --> 00:34:47.590
When I saw him hugging you,

00:34:47.590 --> 00:34:48.920
I honestly lost it.

00:34:49.400 --> 00:34:50.280
I wasn't jealous.

00:34:50.440 --> 00:34:51.440
I was furious.

00:34:51.440 --> 00:34:52.440
He's not good for you.

00:34:52.590 --> 00:34:54.030
Groveling won't be enough.

00:34:54.030 --> 00:34:54.870
I know.

00:34:56.110 --> 00:34:56.950
Honestly,

00:34:57.360 --> 00:34:58.840
you beating him up for me

00:34:59.230 --> 00:35:00.320
felt good.

00:35:06.440 --> 00:35:07.880
It did feel good.

00:35:10.150 --> 00:35:11.320
But now I need to

00:35:11.510 --> 00:35:12.630
deal with what comes next.

00:35:15.760 --> 00:35:16.710
Did your family

00:35:17.550 --> 00:35:18.670
know about this?

00:35:21.920 --> 00:35:23.110
My cousin saw you at her

00:35:23.110 --> 00:35:23.950
photo studio opening.

00:35:25.550 --> 00:35:27.030
I have no idea how.

00:35:27.550 --> 00:35:28.480
She won't say a word.

00:35:39.230 --> 00:35:40.070
Sen,

00:35:43.280 --> 00:35:44.230
I'm serious about this.

00:35:45.880 --> 00:35:47.070
If it's too much for you,

00:35:47.920 --> 00:35:48.760
don't force yourself.

00:35:49.710 --> 00:35:50.630
We can break up.

00:36:10.510 --> 00:36:12.000
Do you want to see that happen?

00:36:19.030 --> 00:36:20.280
Then stop overthinking.

00:36:21.480 --> 00:36:22.510
Forget what others say.

00:36:25.230 --> 00:36:26.710
It's our life.

00:36:30.030 --> 00:36:30.870
Yeah.

00:36:39.800 --> 00:36:40.640
I thought

00:36:40.880 --> 00:36:42.510
the first time I was outside a delivery room

00:36:43.400 --> 00:36:45.400
would be waiting for you to give birth.

00:36:51.060 --> 00:36:54.220
(Delivery Room)

00:37:09.230 --> 00:37:12.590
She's crying. She knows the pain ahead.

00:37:17.320 --> 00:37:19.030
Why is she so ugly?

00:37:20.840 --> 00:37:22.110
I can't tell who she takes after.

00:37:23.000 --> 00:37:23.840
Looks like me.

00:37:44.590 --> 00:37:45.430
Baby,

00:37:46.510 --> 00:37:47.920
Mom and Dad are right here.

00:37:51.920 --> 00:37:52.760
You did great.

00:38:19.880 --> 00:38:21.590
(I'll go to my parents)

00:38:21.800 --> 00:38:22.880
(and your parents.)

00:38:23.030 --> 00:38:24.360
(I'll tell them everything)

00:38:24.360 --> 00:38:26.000
(you've done all these years!)

00:38:33.550 --> 00:38:34.390
Mom,

00:38:35.550 --> 00:38:36.760
still up so late?

00:38:36.760 --> 00:38:38.150
We were just going to bed.

00:38:38.150 --> 00:38:39.880
Why are you calling so late?

00:38:40.110 --> 00:38:41.440
Is Yu there?

00:38:41.880 --> 00:38:43.630
No. What's wrong?

00:38:43.630 --> 00:38:44.630
Did you two fight?

00:38:44.630 --> 00:38:45.920
No, don't worry.

00:38:48.150 --> 00:38:49.030
Alright, got it.

00:38:50.070 --> 00:38:51.070
Have a good rest.

00:38:59.670 --> 00:39:00.510
Hello, Mom.

00:39:01.150 --> 00:39:03.190
Who's ringing me up this late?

00:39:03.190 --> 00:39:04.030
What's wrong?

00:39:04.190 --> 00:39:05.230
I miss you.

00:39:05.510 --> 00:39:06.710
How are you and Dad?

00:39:07.880 --> 00:39:09.360
We are both fine.

00:39:09.670 --> 00:39:10.590
How about you?

00:39:10.590 --> 00:39:12.760
Go to bed early. Don't stay up too late.

00:39:12.960 --> 00:39:13.800
Got it.

00:39:15.190 --> 00:39:16.030
Where's Yu?

00:39:18.280 --> 00:39:20.550
She's not home. Perhaps still at work.

00:39:21.400 --> 00:39:22.840
Still working so late?

00:39:23.110 --> 00:39:24.590
She needs to get good rest.

00:39:25.110 --> 00:39:27.590
Oh, Yu called me a few days ago.

00:39:29.230 --> 00:39:30.150
What did she say?

00:39:31.510 --> 00:39:32.670
She said you two are busy.

00:39:32.840 --> 00:39:34.440
Your dad and I can go on a trip.

00:39:34.440 --> 00:39:36.670
She transferred 8,000 yuan to me,
but I didn't take it.

00:39:37.110 --> 00:39:38.630
Then she sent some supplements.

00:39:38.840 --> 00:39:40.440
I checked. Those are expensive.

00:39:40.960 --> 00:39:43.440
You both work hard
for your money. Don't waste it.

00:39:43.710 --> 00:39:45.960
We have everything here.
No need to buy us stuff.

00:39:46.440 --> 00:39:48.880
Make sure to tell Yu not to waste her money.

00:39:49.670 --> 00:39:50.510
Okay, I will.

00:39:51.320 --> 00:39:52.510
You guys go to bed.

00:39:58.920 --> 00:39:59.840
Thanks,

00:40:01.510 --> 00:40:03.440
can you tell me where your mom is?

00:40:16.880 --> 00:40:17.720
Are you alright?

00:40:18.440 --> 00:40:19.400
I thought you liked me.

00:40:23.480 --> 00:40:24.480
But you're married.

00:40:25.030 --> 00:40:25.870
So what?

00:40:26.960 --> 00:40:27.800
Do you mind?

00:40:28.070 --> 00:40:28.910
Are you chickening out?

00:40:31.960 --> 00:40:33.360
Did he do something to you?

00:40:34.590 --> 00:40:36.190
You can't hurt yourself over him.

00:40:37.590 --> 00:40:39.840
I hate it when you get
all preachy and serious.

00:41:46.190 --> 00:41:47.030
This is for you.

00:41:47.190 --> 00:41:48.400
It's a unicorn.

00:41:48.400 --> 00:41:50.320
It stands for loyalty in love.

00:42:34.710 --> 00:42:36.670
I got you fresh pajamas.

00:42:38.550 --> 00:42:39.390
Don't be afraid.

00:42:41.110 --> 00:42:42.110
Get some rest.

00:43:08.580 --> 00:43:13.380
(Delivery Room)

00:43:19.400 --> 00:43:20.240
This is my daughter.

00:43:21.360 --> 00:43:23.230
(Do you want a boy or a girl?)

00:43:23.400 --> 00:43:24.760
(I want them both,)

00:43:25.070 --> 00:43:26.030
(a boy and a girl.)

00:43:26.030 --> 00:43:27.670
(You wish. Dream on.)

00:43:41.030 --> 00:43:42.070
Doctor, I'll be there in a sec.

00:43:42.280 --> 00:43:43.120
Okay.

00:44:00.590 --> 00:44:01.670
I deleted the post,

00:44:04.230 --> 00:44:05.400
though it might not help much.

00:44:10.320 --> 00:44:11.160
If you need anything

00:44:11.880 --> 00:44:12.920
from the photo studio, I...

00:44:12.920 --> 00:44:13.760
I'm good.

00:44:14.880 --> 00:44:16.480
Get your act together. Be a real man,

00:44:18.510 --> 00:44:19.550
a good husband,

00:44:21.400 --> 00:44:22.240
and a good father.

00:44:28.630 --> 00:44:29.470
Sen,

00:44:29.670 --> 00:44:30.510
let's go home.

00:44:36.910 --> 00:44:41.010
♪Hold your breath to face the lonely sea♪

00:44:41.820 --> 00:44:44.480
♪The surroundings are no longer blue♪

00:44:44.780 --> 00:44:47.660
♪The warmth around me is gone♪

00:44:48.950 --> 00:44:53.170
♪Longing for a sigh to blow away
the dust in my heart♪

00:44:53.690 --> 00:44:56.460
♪Thoughts no longer linger♪

00:44:56.720 --> 00:45:00.000
♪Heartbeat no longer slow♪

00:45:01.300 --> 00:45:04.230
♪In loneliness, I bear...♪

00:45:12.041 --> 00:45:14.640
♪I'll admit♪

00:45:14.641 --> 00:45:18.680
♪My back is faced against the wall♪

00:45:19.561 --> 00:45:23.427
♪There's nothing that
I wouldn't try to do♪

00:45:23.452 --> 00:45:27.640
♪For this feeling to have you♪

00:45:27.921 --> 00:45:30.120
♪I'll resist♪

00:45:30.441 --> 00:45:32.455
♪Your gaze, your lips♪

00:45:32.480 --> 00:45:34.640
♪Your touches again♪

00:45:35.521 --> 00:45:39.501
♪There's no one that
I wouldn't try to fool♪

00:45:39.526 --> 00:45:42.560
♪For an image of you♪

00:45:43.561 --> 00:45:46.000
♪Take my hand again♪

00:45:46.001 --> 00:45:47.760
♪Take my mind again♪

00:45:47.841 --> 00:45:51.200
♪Break into my heart again♪

00:45:51.601 --> 00:45:53.778
♪I'm falling out again♪

00:45:53.803 --> 00:45:55.640
♪I'm on my knees again♪

00:45:55.641 --> 00:45:59.480
♪To beg for the truth♪

00:46:01.321 --> 00:46:05.480
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:46:05.481 --> 00:46:10.480
♪Is that the secret to love♪

00:46:10.841 --> 00:46:13.800
♪I thought it had came from
below us♪

00:46:13.881 --> 00:46:17.280
♪Did it come from above♪

00:46:17.361 --> 00:46:21.120
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:46:21.361 --> 00:46:26.440
♪Is that the secret to love♪

00:46:26.841 --> 00:46:29.280
♪Is it violent or warming, entrancing♪

00:46:29.281 --> 00:46:33.720
♪This secret of love♪